HEADWORD: mantled ground squirrel
<hw>mantled ground squirrel</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A common
black-striped reddish-brown ground squirrel (<spn>Citellus
lateralis</spn>) of western North America, resembling a large
chipmunk.</def>⟦br⟧
